OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fpartly cloudy for most, isolated
OL,7,Fshowers soon dying out. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening in the north overnight with
OL,9,Fpatchy rain arriving by dawn there,
OL,10,Fremaining dry elsewhere.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy periods during the
OL,13,Fmorning with some rain in the north.
OL,14,FBrightening up by the afternoon with
OL,15,Fsome prolonged sunny spells in the
OL,16,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
