OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,6,Fwarm during this period. Friday, very
OL,7,Fwarm with some hazy sunshine. Saturday
OL,8,Fremaining warm with sunny spells.
OL,9,FSunday, bright, sunny and very warm.
